Tiffany Shepis https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tiffany_Shepis 0 Tiffany Shepis (born September 11, 1979) is an American actress from New York City, who has been involved in film-making since the age of 16. She is popularly known as a "scream queen" in several horror films.
